- New PROMPT_VERSION: v0.36.1.0-deepseek-v4-flash (invalidates cache)
- Rewrote EXTRACT_TAKES_PROMPT: structured instructions, explicit weight rules,
  simplified language for DeepSeek compatibility
- Fixed kind enum in ProposedTake: 'fact'|'take'|'bet'|'hunch' -> 'prediction'|'judgment'|'bet'
- Changed modelId fallback: claude-sonnet-4-6 -> deepseek-chat
- Added patches/0004-propose-takes-deepseek.patch for upgrade workflow
